 She was playing truant from school as well, at some time. So we sent her, perhaps misadvisedly, to a private school, and she had a baby when she was 16, which she wanted to keep. I got into trouble for not having her aborted, but she wanted to keep the b
aby. So she wanted to keep the baby, period. I didn\rquote t expect to get stick for \'85
