 well, never mind, it sorted out your friends from your enemies, pretty rapidly! So that\rquote 
s always nice to know where the real strength lies! So she has been working as a care assistant in a home for the severely handicapped, where they have people coming in for respite care. She does nights, because she could work that
 in with a family, and she\rquote s sticking with nights, even though her sons have now grown up. Her daughter, the first one to be born, married two years ago, and has a son, so I\rquote 
ve got a great-grandson. And the two boys are just starting off in university/coll
ege type things, and their mother has told them they can only come home if they get a job. So they do. I mean, they take their finger out and find work, which until she got tough, they didn\rquote t do. But they\rquote re nice enough lads. So that\rquote 
s Kate. 
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid9241263 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 Then Peter is the next one. He\rquote 
