\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 Now, I\rquote m just wondering, one last question before we break, that\rquote 
s a remarkable lot of children to have brought up at the same time as having a professional career.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 
