. So I got the money for it, and thought that I was filling gaps in the first study, in comparison to the first study, like appoint
ing people who could particular facets of the town as their specialist study, whereas it was just happenstance that we did what we did in the first study. 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid11163676 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid9241263 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 
So Ann [Murcott] was to interact with the women, and pay particular attention to that sort of thing
. And Eric [Batstone], who was a strong Labour person, was asked if he would please work with the Conservatives, because Colin [Bell] had bagged working with the Labour people! So there was that sort of political division. I suppose the class backgrounds 
of people were rather different, and there wasn\rquote 
t the same sort of spread that there had been. Then another thing was to see that they had an office, because all the other work was done in a spare room at my house, and I thought really they could deserve to
 have an office and a telephone and a bit more space. 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid11163676 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid9241263 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 
And anyway, I was in Swansea and had young children, and there was no way I could be in Banbury very much. So I put Colin in charge of it, who was senior, because he was older and had done more resear
ch, and he was a brilliant fieldworker, and I already knew that. He was really, really good at gathering, talking to people. But there were manifold problems. I used to go down, quite regularly, and join in, and get reports back and so on.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid11163676 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 How do you see the problems, then?
