\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 Meg:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 I don\rquote t think I disbelieved in them.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 It\rquote s interesting that you say you don\rquote t think it\rquote 
