\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 Meg:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 Was it the Lynds that went back? I think it was. And I think, if I\rquote 
