\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid544046\charrsid1901768 So, you couldn\rquote t bear to live there now, because it\rquote s changed so?
